<div style="border-left:1px solid #EDEDED; border-right:1px solid #EDEDED; background:#DFDFE0; height:1px; margin:0 1px; font-size:0"><a href="/wiki/File:Pix.gif" class="image" title="Pix.gif"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ed/Pix.gif" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></a></div>
