</td>
<td valign="top" width="33%">
<div style="width:100%">
<div class="BGblue1" style="font-size:150%; padding: 5px; border:1px solid #E6ECFD; text-align:center; background:#F3F5FD">Supporting competence</div>
</div>
<div style="width:100%">
<div class="BGblue1" style="padding: 5px; border:1px solid #E6ECFD; text-align:center; background:#E6ECFD; font-size:90%; line-height: 1.1em; height:44px">The Union can carry out actions to support, coordinate or supplement Member States' actions.</div>
